text: Eadgifu or Edgifu (902 – after 955) also known as Edgiva or Ogive () was a daughterLappenberg, pp. 88-89 of Edward the Elder, King of Wessex and England, and his second wife Ælfflæd. She was born in Wessex. == References == Category:10th-century births Category:955 deaths Category:English princesses Category:Carolingian dynasty Category:House of Wessex Category:Kings and Queens consort of France Category:Year of death unknown
title: Eadgifu of Wessex
